cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use ORION, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "ORION: Multi-Theory AI Cognition Indicator Assessment Toolkit"
abstract: >
  Open-source multi-theory AI cognition-indicator assessment toolkit implementing the
  Butlin et al. (2023) 14-indicator framework across 7 theories (IIT, GWT, HOT, RPT,
  PP, AST, Orch-OR). Provides Phi-proxy computation, LLM-as-Judge scoring pipeline,
  bootstrap confidence intervals, and SHA-256 proof chain for reproducibility.
  Does not constitute a claim of phenomenal experience.
authors:
